                            <div id="question7" style="display:none;">
                                    <h3><span class="label label-warning">7</span> Do you have a long time of not seeing your friends because their partner not allow them to.</h3>
                            </div>
                            <div id="question8" style="display:none;">
                                    <h3><span class="label label-warning">8</span> Do you think your friend partner’s behavior have make you feel something is wrong?</h3>
                            </div>
                            <div id="question9" style="display:none;">
                                    <h3><span class="label label-warning">9</span>Does your friend told you that they have been threaten by their partner?</h3>
                            </div>
                            <div id="question10" style="display:none;">
                                    <h3><span class="label label-warning">10</span> Does your friend try to please their partner to avoid quarreling?</h3>
                            </div>
                            <div id="question11" style="display:none;">
                                    <h3><span class="label label-warning">11</span> Does your friends telling you that they feel frustrated, nothing they do can meet their partner’s demand?</h3>
                            </div>
                            <div id="question12" style="display:none;">
                                    <h3>
                                        <span class="label label-warning">12</span>  Does your friend tell you they have been threaten if they try to leave him or her,
                                        they will never see their children, friends or family again?
                                    </h3>
                            </div>
                            <div id="question13" style="display:none;">
                                    <h3><span class="label label-warning">13</span>Does your friend have thingking of suicide?</h3>
                            </div>
